CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 1, 1945 reads: "Hometown Boy - Joseph Lipscomb, National Negro Opera Company singer, was presented at YM and WHA, Tuesday. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Joseph Lipscomb dancing with unknown woman in front of group of dancers for National Negro Opera Company production of "Aida," including Gertrude Harding, Ms. Allen, Miriam Harding, Agnes Norvell, and Patsy Ware
